## [Unreleased]

### Added
- OpenAPI-generated Python client for OGX
- Support for all OGX API endpoints
- Synchronous (`OgxClient`) and asynchronous (`AsyncOgxClient`) clients
- Type-safe Pydantic models for all API objects

