## Version History

Future releases will be documented here with their changes, following semantic versioning:

- **MAJOR** version for incompatible API changes
- **MINOR** version for new functionality in a backward compatible manner
- **PATCH** version for backward compatible bug fixes

## Maintenance Notes

This SDK is automatically generated from the OGX OpenAPI specification. Manual changes
to the generated code will be overwritten on the next generation. To report issues or
request features, please file an issue at: https://github.com/ogx-ai/ogx/issues
